* Usage instructions:
  - add bitbake to your path:
    export PATH=/opt/installer/bitbake/bin:$PATH
  - mount disk to install (rootfs_path)

  - trigger install process:
    IMAGE_INSTALL="what to install" /opt/installer/oe-core/scripts/bb_install /opt/installer/build /opt/installer/pkgdata /opt/installer/feed <rootfs_path> rootfs
    IMAGE_INSTALL="what to install" /opt/installer/oe-core/scripts/bb_install /opt/installer/build /opt/installer/pkgdata /opt/installer/feed <rootfs_path> update

  - trigger query of what is installed:
    /opt/installer/oe-core/scripts/bb_install /opt/installer/build /opt/installer/pkgdata /opt/installer/feed <rootfs_path> query | \
      awk '/^---QUERY START---$/ { start = "1" ; next; } ; { if (start) printf("%s\n", $0) }'

